---
title: Cheesy Turkey Calzones with Garlic Dip
description: Grab the kids and get them to help with tonight's easy cheesy turkey calzones. The DIY garlicky sauce is the ultimate calzone dipper and comes together with just the stir of a spoon. The kids can even mix and match their fillings... it's a win-win dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-turkey-calzones-f6539276.jpg
